Both HSSF and XSSF throw this exception now when there is whitespace between elements and closing parenthesis. I jumped from 3.12 to 3.14 so not sure if this was in 3.13 or not.

    public static void main(String[] args)
    {
        XSSFWorkbook wb = new XSSFWorkbook();
        XSSFSheet sheet = wb.createSheet();
        Row row = sheet.createRow(0);

        Cell cell = row.createCell(0);
        cell.setCellFormula("(4 + 2)"); // This works

        cell = row.createCell(1);
        cell.setCellFormula("( 4 + 2)"); // This works

        cell = row.createCell(2);
        cell.setCellFormula("(4 + 2 )"); // FormulaParseException
    }
